{"tid":1184951,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【狂徒再現】龍運巴士座位插針筒拮傷女乘客 重案組接手調查","createTime":"2019-06-04T03:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:05:50.000Z","uid":52571,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"77251d1d6fd1e6561257663863ee5d177e36da96","tid":1184951,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"ben<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50640a7b9c80d1b89011fbcd2c58df7896754a21","tid":1184951,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"6月9日大家唔好出街"},{"pid":"c6166ad08fdf064fe7af34603e678f0b5574f57e","tid":1184951,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"nben<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9202c0f6fd80d934a7ce72cb42067e4f75142189","tid":1184951,"uid":8968,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7459108535a455be36144df8d57d07710d772e0e","tid":1184951,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"東涌逸東邨巴士總站，早上8時45分，一名年約30歲女乘客乘搭龍運巴士S64X路線，在上層左邊後五排位置，其間被前面座位伸出的一支針筒，拮傷左小腿，女車長代為報警求助，女乘客送院治理，大嶼山警區重案組接手調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息表示，針筒是一般醫療用、針身較細小的類型，被藏在座椅背與座位間隙縫，針嘴伸出，女乘客上車坐在上層左邊後五排近窗的座椅，當時她未有為意「陷阱」，其間「伸腳」，便被前面座椅插住的針筒嘴拮傷，她向車長求助，由車長代為報警。"},{"pid":"8c70cd5ded60acefa6e20ef44ee47f6c66de8bfe","tid":1184951,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9202c0f6fd80d934a7ce72cb42067e4f75142189","tid":1184951,"uid":8968,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/